description: Sin City Snoballs is the only place in the Vegas Valley where you can enjoy Original Baltimore - style Snoballs, Float Snoballs, or an Ice Cream Cookie Sandwich Sundaes. Only the finest premium ingredients go into these uniquely refreshing treats. With 34 (and counting) flavors to choose from and endless options, you can make your snoball as unique and creative as the city itself.
name: Sin City Snoballs and Snacks
